name: Rabin
Lore: 'Ewok. Tamer of beasts. Thief. Loner. Hunter. Survivor.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each Light side icon at same Endor site. Where present, may substitute for a character just selected to be attacked by a creature. When attacking or being attacked, power +2 and may add one destiny.',
